    "body": "I don't think it's currently possible to compile a subset of contracts that are imported in another set of contracts that do not have these optimizations. Specifically, if you have a contract Foo imported into FooTest it isn't possible to optimize Foo but not FooTest, or the other way around. This is tracked in https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/1540 and https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/11787 (also I think it's sort of a dupe of https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/317?) ",
